[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_chief: Resistance cells have attacked three Root Reserve processing facilities.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_chief: Our intelligence indicates their main force will attempt to breach this checkpoint today.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
