[background arg="res://assets/narrative/sasha_capture.png" fade="2.0"]
join supervisor_russet [z_index="1"]
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: Supervisor Russet steps forward, looking unusually confident.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: Thanks to our enhanced security measures, we've already captured several resistance operatives.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: The guards drag a bruised and battered Sasha into view.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: Including our very own Officer Sasha—a traitor who planned to aid the infiltration.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: She looks up, making brief eye contact with you before being forced to her knees.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: Russet addresses the staff coldly. Let this be a lesson about the consequences of betrayal.

join sweet_potato_sasha [z_index="1"]
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
sweet_potato_sasha: Sasha speaks through swollen lips, her voice weak but defiant.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
sweet_potato_sasha: The real traitors are those who feed our people to each other.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
sweet_potato_sasha: One of the guards strikes her, but she continues.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
sweet_potato_sasha: You can't stop the truth! The resistance will prevail! Root Reserve will fall!
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
sweet_potato_sasha: She's dragged away, still shouting. The people will know what's in their food!
leave sweet_potato_sasha

join supervisor_russet [z_index="1"]
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: Russet straightens his uniform. The traitor will be processed immediately.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: A special batch of Root Reserve, made from the very terrorists who sought to destroy it.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
supervisor_russet: Russet smiles, a cold and terrible expression. Poetic justice, wouldn't you say?
leave supervisor_russet

[background arg="res://assets/narrative/checkpoint_maximum_security.png" fade="2.0"]
join security_officer [z_index="1"]
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_officer: You're escorted to your station by armed guards.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_officer: New orders: All border crossings are suspended except for essential personnel.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_officer: Anyone attempting to cross must have Level Alpha clearance with biometric verification.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_officer: The officer places a special scanner on your desk. This device cannot be fooled.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
security_officer: If anyone without proper clearance approaches, sound the alarm immediately.
leave security_officer

[background arg="res://assets/narrative/resistance_operative_approach.png" fade="2.0"]
join resistance_operative [z_index="1"]
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
resistance_operative: Hours into your shift, a potato in official government uniform approaches.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
resistance_operative: They slide their documents across—seemingly perfect Alpha clearance credentials.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
resistance_operative: But as you scan them, a tiny blue identification card falls from inside the folder.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
resistance_operative: The operative gives you a barely perceptible nod. "The roots grow deep."
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
resistance_operative: It's the resistance password. This is one of the infiltrators you were supposed to help.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
resistance_operative: They're continuing the mission despite Sasha's capture.

set {critical_choice} = "none"
- "Process them through, ignoring the scanner alerts" (Help the resistance)
   set {critical_choice} = "help"
- "Sound the alarm immediately" (Betray the resistance)
   set {critical_choice} = "betray"
- "Tell them it's too dangerous and they should leave now" (Warn them)
   set {critical_choice} = "warn"

if {critical_choice} == "help":
   join resistance_operative [z_index="1"]
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: The operative's eyes show momentary relief as you override the scanner.
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: They whisper as they take back their papers: "For Sasha. For Spud."
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: They move through the checkpoint, disappearing down the corridor toward the central database.
   leave resistance_operative

elif {critical_choice} == "betray":
   join resistance_operative [z_index="1"]
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: Horror dawns on the operative's face as you trigger the alarm.
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: "You traitor! We trusted you!" They attempt to flee but are quickly surrounded by guards.
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: As they're dragged away, their eyes lock with yours, filled with betrayal and despair.
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   supervisor_russet: Supervisor Russet appears, looking pleased. "Excellent work. Your loyalty will be rewarded."
   leave resistance_operative

else:
   join resistance_operative [z_index="1"]
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: The operative's face falls as you quietly warn them to leave.
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: "They've got Sasha. They'll process her today. This is our last chance."
   [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
   resistance_operative: Their expression hardens with determination. "I understand your fear, but I'm going through. One way or another."
   leave resistance_operative
   
   set {secondary_choice} = "none"
   - "Fine. I'll help you. Quickly, before someone notices."
      set {secondary_choice} = "relent"
   - "I'm sorry, but I can't be part of this. Goodbye."
      set {secondary_choice} = "refuse"
   
   if {secondary_choice} == "relent":
      join resistance_operative [z_index="1"]
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: The operative nods gratefully as you process them through.
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: "Thank you. Spud will remember those who stood up when it mattered."
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: They hurry through the checkpoint, mission in progress.
      leave resistance_operative
   else:
      join resistance_operative [z_index="1"]
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: The operative looks at you with disappointment and resignation.
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: "Then I have no choice." They suddenly dash past your station.
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: Alarms blare as they sprint down the corridor, guards in pursuit.
      [sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
      resistance_operative: Gunshots echo through the facility. The operative's fate is sealed.
      leave resistance_operative

