[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
player_character: In the confusion, you face a critical decision that will determine your fate and Spud's future.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 3.wav" volume="-5.0"]
player_character: You take a deep breath. It's now or never. I have to make a choice.
[sound path="res://assets/audio/talking/typing on old keyboard 2.wav" volume="-5.0"]
player_character: Do I stay at my post, keep my head down, and pray this all blows over?
